1. Juče je *pobjegao* iz zatvora. (Yesterday he *escaped* from prison.)
2. Kada je vidio pauka, brzo je *pobjegao*. (When he saw the spider, he quickly *ran away*.)
3. Sinoć sam sanjao da sam *pobjegao* od divljih zvijeri. (Last night I dreamt that I *escaped* from wild beasts.)
4. Čim sam čuo da je počeo požar, odmah sam *pobjegao* iz zgrade. (As soon as I heard that the fire started, I immediately *ran away* from the building.)
5. Nije mu bilo lako, ali je uspio *pobjeći* od svog nasilnog partnera. (It wasn't easy for him, but he managed to *escape* from his abusive partner.)
6. Pas je *pobjegao* iz dvorišta i izgubio se u šumi. (The dog *ran away* from the yard and got lost in the forest.)
7. Kada je shvatio da je izgubio novac, brzo je *pobjegao* sa sajma. (When he realized that he lost his money, he quickly *ran away* from the fair.)
8. Nisam znao da je mačka *pobjegla* iz kuće dok se nisam vratio s posla. (I didn't know that the cat *had escaped* from the house until I came back from work.)
9. Otkako je *pobjegao* iz zatvora, niko nije znao gdje se nalazi. (Since he *escaped* from prison, nobody knew where he was.)
10. Dok sam se igrao s mojim psom u parku, slučajno je *pobjegao* i jurio za drugim psom. (While I was playing with my dog in the park, he accidentally *ran away* and chased after another dog.)